WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.260 --> 00:00:03.780
There is a new way to sign into the SAM website.

2
00:00:04.080 --> 00:00:07.460
Your old user name and 
password will no longer work.

3
00:00:08.220 --> 00:00:11.320
The easiest way to get started 
with your new sign in

4
00:00:11.580 --> 00:00:15.360
is to click the "login" button at 
the top of the screen.

5
00:00:15.720 --> 00:00:19.840
Next, click on the "Create an account" button.

6
00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:25.740
A webpage from LOGIN.GOV will 
open up that looks like this page.

7
00:00:26.120 --> 00:00:29.220
Inside, type a strong password.

8
00:00:29.920 --> 00:00:32.840
When you're finished, you can click continue.

9
00:00:32.940 --> 00:00:34.540
Type your phone number in,

10
00:00:34.880 --> 00:00:37.480
and then click "Send code".

11
00:00:38.080 --> 00:00:41.300
On the next screen you will 
be given your personal key.

12
00:00:41.460 --> 00:00:44.480
This key in important for 
accessing the SAM system.

13
00:00:45.180 --> 00:00:48.860
Make sure that you store it in a safe, secure place.

